{"id": "1449267197951344802", "channel_id": "1449167728551133234", "type": 0, "author_id": "476427200015368193", "author_name": "qingming6054", "author_bot": false, "content": "Did some test for Faros, and i believe the problem is, actually there are 2 different types of effects that says \"gain X for every Y\", and the skills' texts didn't make that clear, or even didn't try to make a clarification at all.", "timestamp": "2025-12-13T05:10:26.074000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1449167728551133234", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Faros \"Homesick\" shield scaling talent doesn't benefit from her Soulforge", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1449268555152494683", "channel_id": "1449167728551133234", "type": 0, "author_id": "476427200015368193", "author_name": "qingming6054", "author_bot": false, "content": "For example, Castor's skill \"Umbral Flight\" which gives CritDMG based on Castor's CritDMG, which is equally based on the \"live\" CritDMG which you can see the number in his in-battle panel.", "timestamp": "2025-12-13T05:15:49.656000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1449167728551133234", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Faros \"Homesick\" shield scaling talent doesn't benefit from her Soulforge", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1449269257304019076", "channel_id": "1449167728551133234", "type": 0, "author_id": "476427200015368193", "author_name": "qingming6054", "author_bot": false, "content": "But in the other hand, Horla's Talent \"Writing with Feeling\" strengthens her exalt, based on her Death Resistance, which is NOT influenced by the \"live\" Death Resistance value.", "timestamp": "2025-12-13T05:18:37.062000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1449167728551133234", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Faros \"Homesick\" shield scaling talent doesn't benefit from her Soulforge", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1449271052009214075", "channel_id": "1449167728551133234", "type": 0, "author_id": "476427200015368193", "author_name": "qingming6054", "author_bot": false, "content": "and in Faros' case, i have tried with a team with FMurphy and Faros in, and IDoll as an addition, who can increase \"live\" DMG Amplification in-battle.", "timestamp": "2025-12-13T05:25:44.953000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1449167728551133234", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Faros \"Homesick\" shield scaling talent doesn't benefit from her Soulforge", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1449271503173451907", "channel_id": "1449167728551133234", "type": 0, "author_id": "476427200015368193", "author_name": "qingming6054", "author_bot": false, "content": "So in that test, the shield from Faros' exalt remained the same, no matter i played Elation, or Exalt from IDoll.", "timestamp": "2025-12-13T05:27:32.519000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1449167728551133234", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Faros \"Homesick\" shield scaling talent doesn't benefit from her Soulforge", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1449273264659632148", "channel_id": "1449167728551133234", "type": 0, "author_id": "476427200015368193", "author_name": "qingming6054", "author_bot": false, "content": "So, it can be a bug, or a mistake of description. But I think there are few similar Talent is based on a \"live\" value, it's more likely a text problem.", "timestamp": "2025-12-13T05:34:32.490000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1449167728551133234", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Faros \"Homesick\" shield scaling talent doesn't benefit from her Soulforge", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1449310983632719984", "channel_id": "1449167728551133234", "type": 19, "author_id": "735137568307282011", "author_name": "reya.li", "author_bot": false, "content": "It is not 1:1 comparable to this example because Faros' talent only scales with her own \"personally-contributed\" DMG Amplification (from Covenant, WoDs, Enlighten stats... Soulforge) rather than being affected by the whole team's DMG Amplification (which is also increased by GDoll, GMurphy). This seems normal, or at least how it has worked so far.\n\nWhich is also the same type with Horla's talent scaling, if she somehow had 0% Death Res from \"her own\" stats (not possible but it's just for an example) but the team total was 500%, her talent would give no benefit.\n\nThe problem with Homesick seems simpler and much more likely a bug because it is part of Faros' Soulforge for her to gain +100% DMG Amplification; it is \"her\" stat as with those from her WoDs, Enlightens and Covenants. But it is not being treated as her stat for the purposes of her talent, instead it is functioning more like a hidden relic where the team has the DMG Amp stat increased by 100% after the exploration starts. \n\nIt could still be \"intended\" to be that way and the Soulforge is currently written incorrectly, though given that Faros' talent is also quite weak compared to most stat-scaling talents in the game (I'm not saying that she is weak, but the talent is), it seems plausible that it was supposed to benefit her shield. <:gogogo:1356053074560422118>", "timestamp": "2025-12-13T08:04:25.394000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-13T08:11:04.360000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["476427200015368193"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1449271052009214075", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1449167728551133234", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Faros \"Homesick\" shield scaling talent doesn't benefit from her Soulforge", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1449314745478942830", "channel_id": "1449167728551133234", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "Bug or not, the text really need to be clarified, it doesn't even say that is only Faros AMP that is considered.", "timestamp": "2025-12-13T08:19:22.288000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1449167728551133234", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Faros \"Homesick\" shield scaling talent doesn't benefit from her Soulforge", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
